entries.femaleVariant: Don't be mad at him.
His chakras are all blocked up today. Plus, he's had too much coffee.
And lemme guess – my aura's sputtering?
Mhm. 'Fraid so.
Hey V, I heard… well, your thoughts?
Shouldn't've had to. Sorry 'bout that.
No need to be. I know what's goin' on.
All right, let's go.
Vik's had about enough of me anyway.
Sure, lead the way. Why's this spot special?
I took Jackie there once. It's not far.
Jackie? W-what's he gotta do with any of this?
entries.maleVariant: Jackie? What's he got to do with any of this?

entries.femaleVariant: You'll see. Come on.
He had the same glum face.
<mothertongue l="mex" m="chica" b="\"This is it, " a=". I'm done for.\" "/>
Doesn't sound like the Jackie I knew.
It was a long time ago. His mom'd just found out he'd signed up with the Valentinos.
Trust me. Señora Welles on one shoulder, your gang choombas on the other – no choice can ever seem right.
But he eventually found his way.
See that?
I come here when I need to get away, be alone with my thoughts.
She's onto somethin'. Oughta sit – mull through some shit yourself.
[Sit] Some me time? Hard thing to achieve these days.
Y'know, should call anyone you wanna say goodbye to.
No, but whatever you decide, risk's gonna be high. If things don't go our way…
Just fuckin' do it. Anyone you gotta talk to, now's the time. Pills can wait.
Be alone with my thoughts? Near on unachievable these days…

entries.maleVariant: Hey.
Well, well... Hey, V.
How's things?
Depends what you're askin' about.

entries.femaleVariant: Hey, Judy.
Oh, hey, V.
What's crackin'?
Stayin' outta trouble?
New track comin' along?

entries.maleVariant: Your resolution. Been managin' to stay outta trouble?
Heh. Hasn't been easy.
Yeah. Same here.
The new track – comin' along all right?
Not bad, not bad. Even got a working title.
"Seamurai in Smoke."
Gonna be about our little adventure.
Kerry?
Yeah?
That night… I had a great time.
I'm game for round two if you are. No shortage of boats in the marina.
Yeah, might still get the chance.

entries.femaleVariant: V, uh, everything all right? You... sound strange.

entries.maleVariant: Course, yeah. Just wanted to hear ya.
Mhm.
Well, hey, think I gotta roll.
Sure, sure. Kill it out there, Ker.
You too, V. See ya.

entries.femaleVariant: Just need a minute.
Sorry to wake you.
Won't keep you long. Just... wanted to hear you.
entries.maleVariant: Won't keep you long. Just... wanted to hear ya.

entries.femaleVariant: Hmmm… You picked an interesting hour for it…
V?
OK, what's going on?
Sorry to wake you this late…
entries.maleVariant: S-sorry to wake you this late…

entries.femaleVariant: Is that why you called…? To apologize for interrupting a good night's sleep?
Somethin'... I gotta do today.
Don't know if we'll see each other again.
Dunno that we'll see each other again.
What?!
You know… fine. Fuck off.
No, no, not like that…
Make up your mind.
Time we, uh, went swimmin'...
Hm? Lotta fun, wasn't it?
What you said, then… 'bout what you sensed in me.
entries.maleVariant: What you said, then… about what you sensed in me.

entries.femaleVariant: Death.
Listen, whatever it is you're gonna try…
Just be careful, OK? I'm here waitin'.
Thanks. Do my best.
Wish it'd been anything else.
High time I faced it.
Wish it'd been anything else. Somethin' nice.
Hey, not like it was your fault…
Here's hopin' it comes out better next time.
High time I faced it.
Can't be sure it'll work, but I gotta try.
Mmm, hey…
Panam, hey.
Do you know what time it is…?
Somethin'... Somethin' I gotta do today.
Gonna be high risk, big time. But I have to.
What is it?
It's not for comms, not really.
Then shut up and tell me where you are. In the city?
Yeah.
OK. Then plant your butt somewhere and wait. I'm on my way.
You don't get it, I… I can't wait anymore.
This has something to do with what you were tellin' me before?
You need to take a few deep breaths. Then rethink all this, hard. And then you can call me back. Do you know why? Because I am here for you.
[Call] River.
[Call] Panam.
Nah. Not really my style… goodbyes.
You do you.
Ahh, OK…
Sleep well, my princess.
entries.maleVariant: Sleep well, my prince.

entries.femaleVariant: See you on the other side.
You're up, Johnny. I trust you.
Take the wheel. Just, mh, go easy on us, yeah?
entries.maleVariant: Take the wheel. Just, uh, go easy on us, yeah?

entries.femaleVariant: Thanks, V.
That's right.
Even if I gotta burn this whole fuckin' city down!
Got a feelin' you're gonna regret this decision.
And the moment that dawns, I won't be there to help.
Yeah. Just don't freak out.
Gonna try this with Panam.
We're a lot alike. Trust her more than any of your iron-for-hire choombas.
Have it your way.
See you inside Mikoshi.
[Toss pills] I know. Exactly what we're gonna do.
[Relax fist] OK, dumb idea.
I know.
Exactly why I will do one last thing.
OK, lost me. Realize the shit we've been through to get this far?
Sure do.
To let it all go now? Why?
Cleanest, least bloody option.
We try anything else, people'll die.
People die. It's the way of things.
Am I worth their sacrifice? Are you?
And I know it won't be easy. For either of you.
If you don't wanna decide here, I know a much better place.
Sure. Got a feelin' Vik's had enough of me as is.
Ah, that's more like it – air.
Who, Jack?
There is another option, y'know.
What?
We put all this – the pills, everything – to bed.
If we don't try something, anything, we're both doomed.
'Sides, it's the only way we'll both be aware.
Of what? Death?
Mhm. The moment life escapes.
Hmm. Never really gave it a thought. Funny how you still manage to surprise me sometimes.
Might be somethin' I learned from you.
V, you sure about this?
Long as you got nothin' against it.
Not how I'da done it, but that's all right.
Just like that? No pushback?
Huh, might've learned a little somethin' from you, too.
Is it time?
Y'know, it really is beautiful.
Been nice workin' with ya, V.
Yeah... With you, too, Johnny…
Could be my last ride, this. If it don't work out…
Just wanna be there for it, aware.
You're the one who rejects the only option we got left.
You can let me do that.
My only regret's that I won't get to see how it all ends.
Cooperating with monsters like them – anything's better.
Now, you can let me do that--
Or you can try Panam and her tarmac rats, but then their lives'll weigh heavy on your soul.
Or you take Arasaka's "deal," but then... you'll have your own soul on your conscience.
Or I can take Hanako's offer.
And lose, V. Dammit, there's more at stake here than your life.
Aw, gee, thanks. Got that little faith in me?
entries.maleVariant: Gee, thanks. Got that little faith in me?

entries.femaleVariant: Take your time.
[Sit] Thanks, Misty.
Thanks, Misty. You were right, choice spot.
Take your time.
See, exactly what I mean. Tryna save your sorry hide now.
Exactly what I mean. Here we are now, together, soakin' in this vista of Night City.
My only regret's that I won't get to see how it all ends.
Not in you.
I'll get us through this, you'll see.
[Call] Kerry.
[Call] Judy.
Goodbyes – not my style.
Well, there is this... one stubborn badge.
entries.maleVariant: Well... there is this one stubborn badge.
Well, there is this one musician.

entries.femaleVariant: Judy...
I'm calling Panam.
entries.maleVariant: I'm callin' Panam.

entries.femaleVariant: Panam.
Just wanna hear her voice.
Yeah, even I've grown to like her.
She oughta know that.

entries.maleVariant: Ugh, who, Kerry?
What? Didn't say anything…
Yeah, Kerry.

entries.femaleVariant: Well I'll say one thing – there's always a way out. Here's what you need to do.
Listen, wanna trust Panam and her tarmac rats? Fine. But it'll be their lives weighin' heavy on your soul.
In the rest of 'em.
And if you take Arasaka's "deal"... well, you'll have your own soul on your conscience.
Hey, V.
Hey. I wake you?
entries.maleVariant: Hey. I, uh... wake ya?

entries.femaleVariant: Mh, nah. Wasn't asleep.
Shipping containers again?
Ugh, worse.
What could be worse than that?
Eh, pursuing somebody else's botched case. The feeling you are that fuck-up…
Question is - what're you doing up?
Mighta had a bad dream, too? Like yours.
Just... wanted to hear your voice.
Mighta had a bad dream, too. Kinda like yours.
Just, uh... wanted to hear your voice... officer.
How so?
Also lived a double life.
Mh, as an overweight detective, his moral backbone made of hotdog buns?
Ah, try dead rockerboy with a bloated ego.
entries.maleVariant: Try dead rockerboy with a bloated ego.

entries.femaleVariant: Ooh. Sounds nasty.
Yep. Trade places with me?
Listen... Seein' as you're not asleep, either, whaddaya say to a little nightcap?
I can't.
Not feeling great.
Can't. Not today.
Ah, now's not a great time. Not feelin' well, not at my best.
entries.maleVariant: Now's not a great time, uh... Not feelin' well, not at my best.

entries.femaleVariant: Everything all right?
Fuckin' scared me, know that?
No, still here.
For now.
Worst case scenario – that what you expect?
Thought you were on your way out.
Come a long way to get here, haven't we?
Just think – it all started in a fuckin' landfill.
Mhm. Then you tried to kill me.
Was good you called. Wish I'da had the chance to.
Sure as hell hope it's that and only that.
Mhm.
In that case, ma'am, you have reached the right number.
entries.maleVariant: In that case, you have reached the right number.

entries.femaleVariant: Formerly officer.
Not to me.
Well played.
Wouldn't let me get a word in edgewise.
Prolly for the best. Woulda said too much anyway.
Think trusting Arasaka's risky but worth it.
Gonna ask Panam for help.
Think you and Rogue should go.
Could also just put all this to rest.
Think it's worth takin' a chance on Arasaka.
Gonna try to ask Panam for help.
Think you oughta go with Rogue. Two of you together got the best shot.
[Take omega-blockers] Yep. Gonna do this with the nomads.
[Take pseudoendotrizine] I am. Do your thing, Johnny.
[Take omega-blockers] Yeah. Don't be mad.
Hang on. Need a minute.
And probably not any time soon.
entries.maleVariant: Probably not any time soon.

entries.femaleVariant: Yeah, just got somethin' on my mind.
Y'know, might not've been the best cop in Night City, but I can tell when someone's…
Dunno. Hard to explain.
Talkin' out their ass?
Not speakin' the whole truth.
Found yourself in some trouble, fierce variety.
Mighta been the trouble that found me?
Hey, I gotta go.
Hm, well, that might just be what I like most about you.
Wait, wait. Whatever it is, you can count on me, OK?
I know. Thanks, River. Hang in there.
You absolutely sure? No goin' back on this, y'know.
Just... hold on a minute – need to think.
You heard what she said. Got a way out, always.
Got two words for you – Alt Cunningham. But your call.
OK, not my best idea ever. Forget I mentioned it.
Top floor.
Kinda tough deciding which of your friends get to die, isn't it?
Good news is you got this one choom who's already dead.
And he'd be honored to join you on a wild, suicide run.
You, me and Arasaka Tower. Kinda sounds like a Eurodyne lyric, I know, but trust me – we'll go fuckin' nova.
Suicide run? Not interested.
Let's hear this plan.
This plan, what would it entail, exactly?
Pass. Suicide's not a winning strategy in my book.
Agree to disagree.
"Plan?" Well, might be how Rogue operates.
If Mikoshi's deep underground like Hanako claims it is, you'll just have to find the elevator.
If I gotta die, rather fall into my grave gun in hand and on fire. And not drag anyone down with me.
[Attack Arasaka Tower] Means goin' out with a bang – I like it.
I say you grab the hottest iron you can find, stride in the Tower's front door and cut your own path down to the lower levels.
The more you explain things, the less I like it.
All right – you an' me storm Arasaka Tower.
It does.
But--
End of discussion.
Huh, you just discovered what it takes to become a legend... Grab your iron – let's mobilize.
Honestly, couldn't give a gnat's shit.
The fuck was that?
God, how're you so fuckin' stubborn?
Inherited your finest traits.
entries.maleVariant: Inherited your finer traits.

entries.femaleVariant: Mhm.
Life wasn't easy for my Jackie. But... he found the courage to bet on himself.
After… I brought him here.
What'd Jack decide here?
So what… what'd Jackie decide up here?
Oh, you know…
"Gonna be a legend in this city!"
And I'm gonna leave you alone now.
Could still call Reed. You forget I have that option?
Raising Reed on the holo.
Could raise Reed on the holo – did you forget I have the option?
entries.maleVariant: Could raise Reed on the holo – d'you forget I have the option?

entries.femaleVariant: Nope, no… Field trip to an FIA lab, right? You – cured, me – cut.
Gotta give it a shot, Johnny. Might of the NUSA and all…
Figurin' out somethin' that might work versus a surgical procedure. Choice is clear, Johnny.
entries.maleVariant: Figurin' out somethin' that might work... versus a surgical procedure. Choice is clear, Johnny.

entries.femaleVariant: Didn't forget a thing.
Raisin' Reed on the holo.
So this is how it ends…
Sorry, Johnny, I am. Just… FIA's powerful, gives me the best chance.
We gonna argue about this again? Can we please not?
I get it, I do. Your choice to make, not mine.
Got my pride, V. Not about to beg for my life.
Been nice workin' with ya, Valerie.
entries.maleVariant: Been nice workin' with ya, Vincent.

entries.femaleVariant: Fuck am I sorry.
Gonna argue again?
Gotta be livid with me…
Gotta be livid with me…
Nah, forget about it. Been in it for you to succeed for a while, now…
Just need… a moment to think.
My body, Johnny, plain as that.
How else d'you see it playin' out? It's my body.
Mh, and it's my life.
Damn, you're right. Don't have the heart to to do it.
[Call Reed] Done deal, Johnny, I've decided.
Shit, agreed. Can't do it, wouldn't be right.
Fuck the FIA.
Hah. Good to be seein' eye to eye again.
Thanks, V, truly.
You serious? Wham-bam and no dice?
Wham-bam and no dice.
Hm. Fuckin' shockin' turn of events.
I-- thanks, V. Just thanks.
Say you told the FIA to stick their offer where the sun don't shine?
Just… don't make the call to Reed. We'll find another way.
Do what, now?
Message – didn't see it? They wanna wipe me. Need me to explain the ins and outs?
Shit was clear as day from the start.
Didn't put it all together till now.
C'mon, I was gonna fight to the end, you knew that.
Shit was clear as the summer sky already. D'ya think they'd suck you outta one head, drop you in another?
Well, thought I'd get packed and shelved. And in the best of all possible worlds, that you'd help me hop on the Net.
Not that they'd excise me. Like some fuckin' tumor.
Tsk, yeah. It's just… I didn't put the facts together till now.
Mh. Convenient. But say I go along with that.
Question is, what're you gonna do with the facts?
C'mon, you knew I'd fight for my life to the end, no matter the price. As obvious to you as it was to me.
Call me a chump, but I never thought I'd be that price.
C'mon, V. Don't make the call.
All right, decision time. Raisin' Reed on the holo, tellin' him to dispatch the AV.
So much for your damn promises. "Fuck the FIA, their neural matrix. Just can't do this to you, Johnny." Right…
What the hell, what changed your mind?
Just the better option.
Arasaka's a no-go, can't succeed.
It's just…the better option for me, the best one.
Know how that sounds. Gotta say, I'd be pissed as you in your shoes.
Johnny, c'mon, please. An assault on Arasaka HQ? Successful one? Pipe dream.
I got it done.
I know, I know. Just don't have a... suicide streak.
Don't make me answer, let it go.
You know why. Don't make me answer, go through it all.
